page.title: 14Favourite Foods,Cannington
page.content: My friends have been discussing their favourite foods.The favourite meals are roast dinner, Chinese and Greek food but my favourite meal is cottage pie, ravioli and peas.For breakfast our favourite food is cornflakes,fried breakfast and waffles.I have one boiled egg and some bread.For tea we have pizza,sandwiches,spaghetti and toad in the hole with mashed potato and gravy.For pudding we like french yoghurt, cheese cake, ice cream,apple tart,strawberries and cream and chocalate whip.
